channel.title: Sig i made about a year ago
channel.description:
Gray on gray, yeah, kinda a dumb choice of colors but that's the color the render was and i didn't want to really put gray with other colors because i don't really know what looks good with gray. It's basically a render with text and some c4ds in it, kinda lame and basic and pretty easy to make; there might be some brush strokes in there somewhere but if there are i can't point them out.
[IMG]http://i56.photobucket.com/albums/g198/McNollend/Robo.png[/img]
